<HEADLINE>
<P>
CIF ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
St. Bernard 62, Verbum Dei 61 -- Sophomore forward Chris Keldorf, taking an 
inbounds pass from Terry Sullivan on the right wing, hit a three-point shot at 
the buzzer to lift the Vikings to a Camino Real League victory at home. 
</P>
<P>
Center Wyking Jones scored 19 points and guard Martin Smith added 15 for St. 
Bernard, which snapped a three-game losing streak and improved to 10-10 overall 
and 5-5 in the league. 
</P>
<P>
Verbum Dei fell to 7-11 and 4-6. 
</P>
<P>
St. Anthony 92, Serra 82 -- Despite a game-high 37 points for guard Kenny 
Davis, the Cavaliers suffered an Camino Real League loss at St. Anthony. Serra 
dropped to 9-9 overall and 5-5 in the league. St. Anthony (12-4, 8-2) got 25 
points from center Dan Morgan and 21 from guard Damaine Powell. 
</P>
