Mayweather of Sunny Hills, which won the Freeway League game, 89-75. ; Photo, 
Brett Mitchelson, left, and Terry Mann of Sunny Hills block a shot by 
Fullerton's Ladd Brunner. ALEXANDER GALLARDO / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
